description: This file serves as the entry point for the React-based front-end of a Tic Tac Toe application. It imports React libraries, CSS, and the main App component, then renders the App component inside a React StrictMode wrapper into the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the application into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM element.
